Data set source: 
http://users.jyu.fi/~mapeniem/CVI/Data/  

Description:
Synthetic two dimensional data with five (K = 5) Gaussian and Laplacian 
distributed clusters with different degree of cluster overlap and noise. 
O200 consists of 200 observations and O2000 consists of 2000 observations.  

Reference: 
M. Niemel‰, S. ƒyr‰mˆ, and T. K‰rkk‰inen, "Comparison of cluster validation 
    indices with missing data" In Proceedings of the 26th European Symposium on 
    Artificial Neural Networks, Computational Intelligence and Machine Learning. 
    ESANN, 2018, pp. 461 - 466.

